ygData.messageBody:
highkeep
just past high hold
they have a goblin problem in the basement
you get and exp bonus
in my early 20's i wiped out 3 lvls in one night once
went there at 20, stayed till 34
ther is a bank
bind there or the courtyard (better for those with gate for emergency evac )and shout for group
watch out for trains up into the keep
most of the guards there are corrupt so they wont help you much or will be slow
the ones in the courtyard just at the zone will though

good luck
nomiea winterwolf
44 wood elf druid
xev server, guilded by ancient fellowship
